
## Objective
To set up a virtual lab environment using VirtualBox with Windows Server and Windows 11.

## Steps Performed
- Installed VirtualBox
- Created Windows Server VM
- Created Windows 11 VM
- Configured internal network and allocated CPU, RAM, and storage resources

## Why This Matters
Virtualization is widely used in IT environments for testing and training without affecting production systems.

The Outcome
Two virtual machines successfully created and configured for lab environment.

